{
  "texts": [
    "Style GAN and style 2A Style-Based Generator Framework for Adversarial Networks,\" which employs the advancement of ProGAN in combination with image style transfer and adaptive instance normalization (AdaIN), allows for control over the style of the pictures that are created.",
    "A Mapping network, which maps the input to an intermediate Latent space, is the underpinning of the Style GAN architecture.",
    "After each layer, the intermediate is then processed by the AdaIN, and there are around 18 convolutional layers total.",
    "Style 2 GAN has various enhancements over the original StyleGAN, including normalization, gradually increasing and regularization approaches, etc.",
    "Fig. 14 To generate highly realistic faces using Progressive Growing GAN [34] SR-GAN (Super Resolution GAN)The primary objective of this particular category of GAN is to improve the level of detail in an image that has a lower resolution."
  ]
}